Package: comparepdf
Title: Pixel-Level PDF Comparison Tool
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R:
    person("Edward", "Frankenberger", email = "edward.frankenberger@nih.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Compare PDF documents page-by-page at the pixel level. Renders
    PDF pages to images, computes pixel differences with configurable fuzz
    tolerance, and generates self-contained HTML diff reports with
    visualizations.
License: TBD
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    base64enc,
    pdftools (>= 3.0.0),
    magick (>= 2.7.0),
    cli (>= 3.6.0),
    fs (>= 1.6.0)
